Porechop for adapter trimming.
Trimmomatic for additional read trimming.
Minimap2 for alignment.
Samtools for manipulating alignment files.
iVar for variant calling and consensus generation.
Medaka for polishing.
MAFFT for multiple sequence alignment.
IQ-TREE for phylogenetic tree construction.

envs/trimming.yml
name: trimming
channels:
      - bioconda
      - conda-forge
dependencies:
      - porechop
      - trimmomatic

envs/alignment.yml
name: alignment
channels:
      - bioconda
      - conda-forge
dependencies:
     - minimap2
     - samtools

envs/variant_calling.yml
name: variant_calling
channels:
    - bioconda
    - conda-forge
dependencies:
    - samtools
    - bcftools
    - ivar

envs/polishing.yml
name: polishing
channels:
    - bioconda
    - conda-forge
dependencies:
    - medaka

envs/msa.yml
name: msa
channels:
    - bioconda
    - conda-forge
dependencies:
     - mafft

envs/phylogeny.yml
name: phylogeny
channels:
    - bioconda
    - conda-forge
dependencies:
    - iqtree
